{"tid":573290,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《黑鏡》成真！AI複製人類思想　讓死去親友「復活」","createTime":"2018-02-26T10:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T05:29:05.000Z","uid":22675,"like":71,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"aefd2ef8b8067ef77e8d7e5c64933bd732479bed","tid":573290,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:36:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2785/d2785336.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2785%2Fd2785336.jpg&h=c4dca35b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲科學家利用AI技術，計畫打造出具有人類意識的機器複製人。（圖／示意圖／達志影像）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\r\n<br />\r\n隨著人工智慧(Artificial Intelligence, AI)相關技術的發展，瑞典科學家認為，能用AI完整複製出與逝者一模一樣的「機器複製人」，讓人們能有機會與摯愛的親友再次交談，除此之外，複製人還有可能像蘋果Siri或是亞馬遜Alexa一樣，進行查詢天氣或是報時等其他服務，成為新一代的語音助手，這項技術若是繼續發展，將有可能成為Netflix影集《黑鏡》故事中，打造出具有人類意識的複製人。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n英國《每日郵報》引述俄羅斯Sputnik News報導，瑞典科學家目前正在募集志願者，願意提供他們死去的親友作為研究，利用人工智慧技術重建死者的聲音，未來還有計畫打造機器複製人，透過這種方式，家人不但能再與複製人對話，還可以進行實質的身體接觸，這聽起來像是科幻小說中才會出現的計畫，若能真的實現，數碼永生(Digital Immortality)將會成為我們未來社會的現實。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2703/d2703496.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2703%2Fd2703496.jpg&h=edf29705&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n▲科學家認為AI結合機器人科技，能讓已逝親友以另外一種形式「復活」。（圖／示意圖／視覺中國）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n英國Daily Star報導，加拿大懷雅遜大學(Ryerson University)與麻省理工實驗室的拉赫納馬(Hossein Rahnama)教授去年也曾提出類似概念，命名為「增強永生」(augmented-eternity)，同樣利用人工智慧學習人類在臉書、Snapchat、電子郵件等文字訊息，建構資料庫複製出那個人的思考模式與語氣，打造已逝者的「數位副本」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n拉赫納馬認為，這項技術除了用來紀念逝去親友，還可以應用在教育上，例如讓學生向歷史人物發問、進行對話，由於AI技術能夠持續進化，也代表著「複製人」不會只是人類的死亡副本，他們將會持續累積知識，來應對現代新的議題。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n▼加拿大已有科學團隊，針對人類在網路上的所有訊息進行複製，打造出該人的「數位副本」。（圖／示意圖／視覺中國）<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2962/d2962550.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2962%2Fd2962550.jpg&h=eb991168&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n原文網址: 《黑鏡》成真！AI複製人類思想　讓死去親友「復活」　 | ETtoday新奇 | ETtoday新聞雲 <a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180226/1119649.htm#ixzz58Cs5lEoI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20180226%2F1119649.htm%23ixzz58Cs5lEoI&d=5L0f0P31qWqUGS%2FEmTu3LC7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=527d961b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20180226/1119649.htm#ixzz58Cs5lEoI</a> <br />\r\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook[/quote]"},{"pid":"32d9c1779c916b06f1646e8832c4d237856a08e3","tid":573290,"uid":34777,"like":172,"dislike":1,"score":171,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:37:06.000Z","msg":"最後女主角個結局其實都唔好受<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50c237bde0f07e31034fc507fd53cb540b59ceb","tid":573290,"uid":116289,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:37:32.000Z","msg":"攻殼電子腦"},{"pid":"bd96a17d54c6d5273909dac288d230829fa720a9","tid":573290,"uid":143582,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"複製教主出黎打救apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbbc0cea8b10afaddfa8715d350a705ac5d23513","tid":573290,"uid":48222,"like":31,"dislike":4,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:46:19.000Z","msg":"複製10個女神出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a1bb679a5f9c0ae9354ec663b873f3d46fdc3a","tid":573290,"uid":37933,"like":174,"dislike":3,"score":171,"quote":{"pid":"bd96a17d54c6d5273909dac288d230829fa720a9","tid":573290,"uid":143582,"like":115,"dislike":0,"score":115,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:38:42.000Z","msg":"複製教主出黎打救apple<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-26T10:48:36.000Z","msg":"教主番生應該會整個orange出黎<br />\n救apple都晒藥費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 